{"tid":731252,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"招人玩終極動員令:絕命時刻 (C&C: Zero Hour) - 內含所有C&C遊戲(豪華典藏版)下載","createTime":"2018-07-06T05:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T06:03:32.000Z","uid":119696,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5fdfed7d28b1b123a60fc00c4adc138b00d3e72c","tid":731252,"uid":119696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thepcgames.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Command-and-Conquer-Generals-Zero-Hour-PC-Game-Free-Download4-min-1024x768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthepcgames.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FCommand-and-Conquer-Generals-Zero-Hour-PC-Game-Free-Download4-min-1024x768.jpg&h=32b085e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.oldpcgaming.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Snap92_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.oldpcgaming.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2FSnap92_1.jpg&h=b4ce3e24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.monx007.com/pelengkap/generals6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.monx007.com%2Fpelengkap%2Fgenerals6.jpg&h=3a8dcf55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/GVUY6HmR-3E/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FGVUY6HmR-3E%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=f8ed555d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢排屎忽痕想玩返呢隻以前細個玩ge GAME (果時日日單機都不亦樂乎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，先發現官方伺服一早已經關閉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係原來有忠實玩家自己整左個SERVER，經觀察高峰期絕命時刻 有70幾人上線...都唔少人玩緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想試下招返亞洲人玩返呢隻高質舊GAME <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢兩晚係到研究點樣可以玩線上對戰，中間出現好多ERROR全部解決晒，趁住記得整個教學出黎順便重新上傳同集中返一d重要檔案 (好多無SEED, 死LINK)，希望隻好GAME得以保存。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>主體遊戲下載</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n首先請不要做乞衣，支持正版其實可以去origin購買豪華典藏版下載(HK$160)，間中會有特價，之前半價HK$80我miss左，至於我自己就好耐之前一早下載左成套落黎咁就無謂浪費，convert做ISO上載左去Google Drive﹕<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1-BkKbHGzHNIm6NeV35U3DFadbuTghlNZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1-BkKbHGzHNIm6NeV35U3DFadbuTghlNZ&d=xHFVjRPohI8qIoRYiaf%2FEjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=815ab81b\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1-BkKbHGzHNIm6NeV35U3DFadbuTghlNZ</a><br />\n<br />\n主題遊戲全部英文版，將軍+Zero Hour繁中補丁見下。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Zero Hour安裝教學</strong></span>﹕<br />\n<br />\n1. 用Daemon Tool 掛載ISO image<br />\n<br />\n2. 由於今次重點是Zero Hour, 開啟Setup選擇要安裝的C&amp;C 遊戲 (General + Zero Hour)<br />\n<br />\n3. 安裝最新遊戲補丁：<br />\n     將軍1.08﹕<a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/ngx46z7t1sx2tdd/Generals-108-english.exe?dl=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropbox.com%2Fs%2Fngx46z7t1sx2tdd%2FGenerals-108-english.exe%3Fdl%3D0&d=xHFVjRPohI8qIoRYiaf%2FEjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e45521af\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dropbox.com/s/ngx46z7t1sx2tdd/Generals-108-english.exe?dl=0</a>    (如果只玩Zero Hour，不必下載此檔案)<br />\n<br />\n   Zero Hour 1.04: <a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/kc83mg4ng18e5kg/GeneralsZH-104-english.exe?dl=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropbox.com%2Fs%2Fkc83mg4ng18e5kg%2FGeneralsZH-104-english.exe%3Fdl%3D0&d=xHFVjRPohI8qIoRYiaf%2FEjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=fb0218cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dropbox.com/s/kc83mg4ng18e5kg/GeneralsZH-104-english.exe?dl=0</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 如果Zero Hour安裝遊戲補丁半途出現錯誤，可以退出並使用升級所需的原始檔先覆蓋原始檔案，然後再次升級。原始檔﹕<a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/sh/swa2gmvtikmz82c/AABHeyw0yQ-wW2RvNiai4D7Ua?dl=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropbox.com%2Fsh%2Fswa2gmvtikmz82c%2FAABHeyw0yQ-wW2RvNiai4D7Ua%3Fdl%3D0&d=xHFVjRPohI8qIoRYiaf%2FEjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b44b8c54\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dropbox.com/sh/swa2gmvtikmz82c/AABHeyw0yQ-wW2RvNiai4D7Ua?dl=0</a><br />\n<br />\n預設原始檔案路徑﹕C:\\Program Files (x86)\\EA Games\\Command &amp; Conquer The First Decade\\Command &amp; Conquer(tm) Generals Zero Hour<br />\n<br />\n5. 安裝Zero Hour免CD補丁﹕<a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/sh/258yp8vjewoxqbx/AAA5ez3n-dqQvn7UVR-kgKGra?dl=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropbox.com%2Fsh%2F258yp8vjewoxqbx%2FAAA5ez3n-dqQvn7UVR-kgKGra%3Fdl%3D0&d=xHFVjRPohI8qIoRYiaf%2FEjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=7115d735\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dropbox.com/sh/258yp8vjewoxqbx/AAA5ez3n-dqQvn7UVR-kgKGra?dl=0</a>        <span style=\"color: red;\">為了能夠線上對戰，請不要copy game.dat，只需要把generals.exe取代原有的檔案 (我是這樣做就OK)</span>。<br />\n<br />\n6. 然後安裝繁中補丁﹕<a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/sh/wi38mxuie6d4uqw/AABdmYCSTKthseVqGO__RUd-a?dl=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropbox.com%2Fsh%2Fwi38mxuie6d4uqw%2FAABdmYCSTKthseVqGO__RUd-a%3Fdl%3D0&d=xHFVjRPohI8qIoRYiaf%2FEjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=79ca61ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dropbox.com/sh/wi38mxuie6d4uqw/AABdmYCSTKthseVqGO__RUd-a?dl=0</a>   <br />\n解壓檔案到C:\\Program Files (x86)\\EA Games\\Command &amp; Conquer The First Decade\\Command &amp; Conquer(tm) Generals Zero Hour\\Data\\English(可連線大廳)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">運行遊戲</span></strong><br />\n1. 運行遊戲前有可能需要先去C:\\Program Files (x86)\\EA Games\\Command &amp; Conquer The First Decade\\Command &amp; Conquer(tm) Generals Zero Hour，右鍵選general.exe &gt; compatibility &gt; 以Windows XP (service pack 3)運行，並且勾選以administrator 權限去運行。<br />\n<br />\n2.  你亦有可能需要把防毒關掉或加添例外，否則可能會出現&quot;DirectX 8.1&quot; 或 &quot;File corruped&quot; 的錯誤，我自己而言必須關掉Bitdefender的Advanced Threat Defence才可以運行，其他防毒功能可以維持開啟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">線上對戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong>﹕<br />\n<br />\n線上對戰有兩個平台，分別係Cnc-online同外國版V-lan 的 GameRanger，CNC 採用官方連線方式，而GameRanger就用直接連線方式，GameRanger都好多人keep住開場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">Cnc-online:</span></strong><br />\n1. 去cnc-online申請帳戶及 下載 C&amp;C Online Launcher: <a href=\"https://cnc-online.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcnc-online.net%2F&d=xHFVjRPohI8qIoRYiaf%2FEjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=34192dde\" target=\"_blank\">https://cnc-online.net/</a><br />\n    英文教學見這裡﹕<a href=\"https://cnc-online.net/en/setup/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcnc-online.net%2Fen%2Fsetup%2F&d=xHFVjRPohI8qIoRYiaf%2FEjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=d091acf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://cnc-online.net/en/setup/</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 第一次使用請運行C&amp;C Online Launcher，然後勾選Hook功能，以後可以直接運行Zero Hour而無須手動開啟C&amp;C online launcher 。由於是次安裝是豪華版，launcher直接按Zero Hour是無法運行，必須要使用hook功能。<br />\n<br />\n3. 若跟從上述步驟，你已經安裝了最新補丁，無須再次安裝補丁，你可以安裝Gentool提升遊戲體驗(非必要，實際用途還在發掘中...)<br />\n<br />\n4. 開啟遊戲 &gt; multiplayer mode&gt; Online Game &gt; 輸入你在cnc-online註冊的電郵、匿稱及伺服密碼 即可<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">GameRanger 請參看這教學影片</span>:  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MlYrlE1CG8g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMlYrlE1CG8g&d=xHFVjRPohI8qIoRYiaf%2FEjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=5dd1d20f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MlYrlE1CG8g</a>     經測試可以與hooked Cnc-online launcher 兩者並用<br />\n<br />\n歡迎發問<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8803314a2a7e71f850d8da7d6ad2cdbec1d9da42","tid":731252,"uid":119696,"like":0,"d